"use strict";(self.webpackChunkPradocument=self.webpackChunkPradocument||[]).push([[8417],{4080:(s,e,n)=>{n.r(e),n.d(e,{data:()=>a});const a={key:"v-0b522d24",path:"/knowledge/Deepin/%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90SSH%E5%85%AC%E7%A7%81%E9%92%A5%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE.html",title:"deepin(Linux)中安装git,生成SSH公私钥配置Gitee，GitHub(2020.11)",lang:"en-US",frontmatter:{},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"1. 输入命令安装git",slug:"_1-输入命令安装git",children:[]},{level:2,title:"2. 然后进行使用git之前需要做的最小配置",slug:"_2-然后进行使用git之前需要做的最小配置",children:[]},{level:2,title:"3. 生成SSH公私钥",slug:"_3-生成ssh公私钥",children:[]},{level:2,title:"4. 然后进入.ssh文件夹",slug:"_4-然后进入-ssh文件夹",children:[]},{level:2,title:"注意点",slug:"注意点",children:[]}],filePathRelative:"knowledge/Deepin/生成SSH公私钥配置.md",git:{updatedTime:1657620056e3,contributors:[{name:"孤城致幻",email:"Xast@123456",commits:1}]}}},3111:(s,e,n)=>{n.r(e),n.d(e,{default:()=>c});var a=n(6252);const i=(0,a.uE)('<h1 id="deepin-linux-中安装git-生成ssh公私钥配置gitee-github-2020-11" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#deepin-linux-中安装git-生成ssh公私钥配置gitee-github-2020-11" aria-hidden="true">#</a> deepin(Linux)中安装git,生成SSH公私钥配置Gitee，GitHub(2020.11)</h1><blockquote><p>Linux下就不要再费劲去找win下的那种图形化工具一直“下一步”“下一步”的去安装了（ps：官方教程上也是用的命令行） 今天需要用到gitee,然后查找各种教程安装，博客视频都有看，因为说的都有些区别，花费了好长时间对比，所以想总结一个完整的，以免看到一大堆不太一样的教程再去纠结选哪个。</p></blockquote><h2 id="_1-输入命令安装git" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-输入命令安装git" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 1. 输入命令安装git</h2><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">apt</span> <span class="token function">install</span> git-all\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><h2 id="_2-然后进行使用git之前需要做的最小配置" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-然后进行使用git之前需要做的最小配置" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 2. 然后进行使用git之前需要做的最小配置</h2><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">git</span> config --global user.name <span class="token string">&quot;your_name&quot;</span>\n<span class="token function">git</span> config --global user.email <span class="token string">&quot;xxxxx@youremail.com&quot;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><h2 id="_3-生成ssh公私钥" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-生成ssh公私钥" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 3. 生成SSH公私钥</h2><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code> ssh-keygen -t rsa -b <span class="token number">4096</span> -C <span class="token string">&quot;xxxx@youremail.com&quot;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><blockquote><p>然后会有3条命令提示，直接回车确认就好</p></blockquote><h2 id="_4-然后进入-ssh文件夹" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-然后进入-ssh文件夹" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4. 然后进入.ssh文件夹</h2><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token builtin class-name">cd</span> ~/.ssh\n<span class="token function">ls</span> -al\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><p>以下两个文件即为公私钥</p><div class="language-text ext-text line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-text"><code>id_rsa #私钥\nid_rsa.pub #公钥\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><p>执行命令</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">cat</span> id_rsa.pub\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>然后一大串的那个即为公钥，复制粘贴到gitee,github等即可配置完成</p><p>配置好公私钥之后 输入命令测试是否配置成功</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">ssh</span> -T git@gitee.com\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>第一次测试会提示是否继续连接，输入yes,之后再进行就不会了在询问了 如该测试失败提示<code>Permission denied, please try again.</code>，则仔细看下方的注意点，照做</p><h2 id="注意点" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#注意点" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 注意点</h2><p>使用公钥(id_rsa.pub)链接线上仓库认证，本地GIT仓库也需要使用ssh链接方式 如该配置了公钥，pull代码还需要输入帐号密码，则去当前本地仓库根目录找到.git &gt; config 文件修改以下内容</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 找到[remote &quot;origin&quot;] 这一行</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">[</span>remote <span class="token string">&quot;origin&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>\n\turl <span class="token operator">=</span> root@gitxxxxx.git\n\tfetch <span class="token operator">=</span> +refs/heads/*:refs/remotes/origin/*\n\t\n<span class="token comment"># 修改url的仓库地址为ssh地址</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br></div></div>',22),t={href:"https://docs.github.com/cn/authentication/connecting-to-github-with-ssh/testing-your-ssh-connection",target:"_blank",rel:"noopener noreferrer"},l=(0,a.Uk)("git密钥教程"),r={},c=(0,n(3744).Z)(r,[["render",function(s,e){const n=(0,a.up)("OutboundLink");return(0,a.wg)(),(0,a.iD)(a.HY,null,[i,(0,a._)("p",null,[(0,a._)("a",t,[l,(0,a.Wm)(n)])])],64)}]])},3744:(s,e)=>{e.Z=(s,e)=>{const n=s.__vccOpts||s;for(const[s,a]of e)n[s]=a;return n}}}]);